---
// Pricing.astro - Pricing section with 3 plans
---

<section class="section" id="harga" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="section-tag" data-i18n="pricing_tag">Investasi</div>
  <h2><span data-i18n="pricing_h2_line1">Harga Transparan,</span><br /><em data-i18n="pricing_h2_em">Tanpa Biaya Tersembunyi</em></h2>
  <p class="section-lead" data-i18n="pricing_lead">
    Pilih paket yang sesuai kebutuhan. Semua paket termasuk source code — Anda
    memiliki sistem sepenuhnya.
  </p>

  <div class="pricing-grid">
    <!-- Plan 1: Self Hosted -->
    <div class="pricing-card reveal">
      <div class="price-tier" data-i18n="plan1_tier">Self Hosted</div>
      <div class="price-num">
        <span data-i18n="plan1_price">Rp 1,5jt</span>
        <span class="period" data-i18n="plan1_period">/ sekali bayar</span>
      </div>
      <div class="price-desc" data-i18n="plan1_desc">Source code lengkap Node.js + Docker. Deploy di server sendiri. Support instalasi via dokumentasi.</div>
      <ul class="price-features">
        <li data-i18n="plan1_f1">Source code penuh (Node.js)</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan1_f2">Docker Compose config</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan1_f3">Admin Dashboard React</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan1_f4">Dokumentasi instalasi</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan1_f5">1 bulan support email</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan1_f6">Update minor gratis</li>
      </ul>
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/6289670005828?text=Halo,%20saya%20tertarik%20paket%20Self%20Hosted%20WA%20Order"
        class="btn-card btn-card-outline"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        data-i18n="pricing_btn"
        data-wa-key="pricing_wa1"
      >
        Pesan Sekarang
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Plan 2: WordPress Plugin (Featured) -->
    <div class="pricing-card reveal featured">
      <div class="price-tier" data-i18n="plan2_tier">WordPress Theme</div>
      <div class="price-num">
        <span data-i18n="plan2_price">Rp 800rb</span>
        <span class="period" data-i18n="plan2_period">/ sekali bayar</span>
      </div>
      <div class="price-desc" data-i18n="plan2_desc">Tema WordPress siap pakai. One click install dalam 5 menit. Cocok untuk pemilik toko web yang ingin terima order via WA.</div>
      <ul class="price-features">
        <li data-i18n="plan2_f1">File tema .zip</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan2_f2">Katalog & cart bawaan</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan2_f3">Tombol order di produk</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan2_f4">Notifikasi admin WA</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan2_f5">Template pesan kustom</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan2_f6">3 bulan support</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan2_f7">Update gratis 1 tahun</li>
      </ul>
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/6289670005828?text=Halo,%20saya%20tertarik%20paket%20WordPress%20Theme%20WA%20Order"
        class="btn-card btn-card-solid"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        data-i18n="pricing_btn"
        data-wa-key="pricing_wa2"
      >
        Pesan Sekarang
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Plan 3: Odoo Module -->
    <div class="pricing-card reveal">
      <div class="price-tier" data-i18n="plan3_tier">Odoo Module</div>
      <div class="price-num">
        <span data-i18n="plan3_price">Rp 3jt</span>
        <span class="period" data-i18n="plan3_period">/ sekali bayar</span>
      </div>
      <div class="price-desc" data-i18n="plan3_desc">Modul Odoo 16/17 terintegrasi penuh dengan Sales, Invoice, dan Inventory. Untuk bisnis skala menengah ke atas.</div>
      <ul class="price-features">
        <li data-i18n="plan3_f1">Modul Odoo 16 & 17</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan3_f2">Integrasi Sales & Invoice</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan3_f3">Notif status pengiriman</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan3_f4">Multi-company support</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan3_f5">Instalasi oleh tim kami</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan3_f6">3 bulan support penuh</li>
        <li data-i18n="plan3_f7">Customisasi minor gratis</li>
      </ul>
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/6289670005828?text=Halo,%20saya%20tertarik%20modul%20Odoo%20WA%20Order"
        class="btn-card btn-card-outline"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        data-i18n="pricing_btn"
        data-wa-key="pricing_wa3"
      >
        Pesan Sekarang
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
    padding: 6rem 3rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .section-tag::before {
    content: "";
    width: 20px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--green);
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .section-lead {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 242, 232, 0.08);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .pricing-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .pricing-card.featured {
    border-color: var(--green);
    background: rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.04);
  }

  .pricing-card.featured::before {
    content: attr(data-popular-label);
    position: absolute;
    top: -1px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%);
    background: var(--green);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-family: "Syne", sans-serif;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .price-tier {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .price-num {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .price-num .period {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: "DM Mono", monospace;
  }

  .price-desc {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245, 242, 232, 0.06);
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .price-features {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .price-features li {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: rgba(245, 242, 232, 0.7);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .price-features li::before {
    content: "→";
    color: var(--green);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
  }

  .btn-card {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-family: "Syne", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-card-outline {
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 242, 232, 0.2);
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .btn-card-outline:hover {
    border-color: var(--green);
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .btn-card-solid {
    background: var(--green);
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .btn-card-solid:hover {
    background: var(--lime);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .pricing-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
